msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>All the <2.se_co>sand seals outside <3.re_co>haven't been\n"
"trained, which means they'll run\n"
"away the moment you dismount.\n"
"But these ones—the ones that Frelly\n"
"trained—they'll wait patiently for their\n"
"master.\n"
"All of the <4.se_co>sand seals<5.re_co> used in the <6.se_co>sand-\n"
"seal races<7.re_co> were trained by Frelly, too.<8.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: sound
msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Annnnd done!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>What with preparing their meals, cleaning\n"
"up after them, and everything else, the\n"
"day just seems to fly by!\n"
"It never feels like I'm done, either.<3.pa> <4.se_co>If I lay\n"
"out food, they'll rush over as fast as they\n"
"can... <5.re_co>Even if I just fed them!\n"
"<6.so>I swear, they have bottomless pits in\n"
"place of stomachs..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "Talk_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>All right! I'm gonna do my best at my\n"
"part-time job!\n"
"\n"
"It's actually really tough taking care of\n"
"the <2.se_co>sand seals<3.re_co>,<4.pa> but seeing how happy\n"
"they are when their food is put out...\n"
"Although, I do sometimes put out too\n"
"much food...\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>I'm so exhausted when the day is over."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (longer)
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
