msgctxt "Talk_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The <2.se_co>sand seals<3.re_co> here were all trained\n"
"by Frelly. They're faster, and they'll wait\n"
"for you to return to them.\n"
"By comparison, the ones outside who\n"
"haven't been trained will just run off the\n"
"moment you dismount.\n"
"It's definitely worth renting a trained\n"
"one! Frelly puts her heart into training\n"
"them!<4.pa>\n"
"Frelly trained the sand seals used in the\n"
"<5.se_co>sand-seal races<6.re_co> too, of course.<7.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm so tired...\n"
"Please let me rest right now."
msgstr ""

