msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The <2.se_co>sand-seal races <3.re_co>are a Gerudo\n"
"tradition...\n"
"\n"
"It's pretty simple: you use a <4.se_co>sand seal<5.re_co> to\n"
"race around a course to see who's the\n"
"fastest.\n"
"Just go out the <6.se_co>southeast gate<7.re_co> of the\n"
"town and head to the right. You'll see\n"
"the starting line immediately!\n"
"No harm in taking a peek, right?"
msgstr ""

